== 大众文化 ==
# [[英国|英国]]女演员{{tsl|en|Sally Lindsay|塞利·林德西}}曾经在一次慈善赛的间隙与EJ10合影时，硬生生坐碎了赛车车体。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://auto.qq.com/a/20050223/000025.htm|title=英国女星体重过大坐碎乔丹车队F1赛车|accessdate=2009-03-11|publisher=qq.com|archive-date=2005-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050307121519/http://auto.qq.com/a/20050223/000025.htm}}</ref>

